Package: modellator
Title: Automatic deployment of a statistical model; from data to reporting.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Antonio", "Rebordao", email = "antonio.rebordao@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A set of utilities to create, setup, train and test a statistical
    model in an automatic fashion. Also generates reports that can be easily
    customized to the users' needs.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
